"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?26/37/27224?source=see_link\">",
"      Symptomatic relief of sore throat in children and adolescents",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?34/22/35178?source=see_link\">",
"      Tonsillectomy and adenoidectomy in children",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
